<li><a href="http://grove.ufl.edu/~psy4930/" class="external text" title="http://grove.ufl.edu/~psy4930/" rel="nofollow">A survey course</a> at <a href="/wiki/University_of_Florida" title="University of Florida">University of Florida</a></li>
<li>Edinburgh <a href="http://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~charles/thesis/Fox_Consciousness_Thesis.ps" class="external text" title="http://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~charles/thesis/Fox_Consciousness_Thesis.ps" rel="nofollow">thesis</a> (.ps) on consciousness including up-to-date reviews</li>
